        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrogenation reaction",
        "description": "在280°C和4 MPa氢气压力下，使用5Ni-20WO3/Al2O3和Beta沸石组成的串联催化剂，在高压釜中催化加氢裂化聚乙烯(PE)废物。反应4小时后，PE转化率达到87.2%，主要生成C5-C20液体烷烃，选择性约为88%。",
        "text_snippet": "The hydrocracking reaction of polyolefin was carried out in an electrically heated stainless steel high-pressure autoclave... In a typical test, 8.0 g PE, 0.2 g 5Ni-20WO3/Al2O3 and 0.2 g Beta zeolite were added into the autoclave... The temperature was set as 280 °C for 4 h... reaching a yield of 77.8 % to gasoline-jet ranged liquid hydrocarbons (mainly C5-C16 and minor C16+)",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      }
    ]
